<lb n="0709a07" ed="T"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="open"><cb:mulu n="001" type="卷"/><cb:jhead><note n="0709002" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">【原】麗本，【甲】長治二年寫高山寺藏本，【乙】高山寺藏古寫本，【丙】久安二年寫高山寺藏本</note>金剛頂超勝三界經說文殊<note n="0709003" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（五字…卷）八字＝（師利菩薩祕密心真言）九字【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><note n="0709003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（五字…卷）八字【大】，師利菩薩祕密心真言【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app cb:word-count="8" n="0709003"><lem wit="【大】">五
<lb n="0709a08" ed="T"/>字真言勝相<note n="0709004" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔一卷〕－【明】＊</note><note n="0709004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">一卷【大】＊，〔－〕【明】＊</note><app n="0709004"><lem wit="【大】">一卷</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】">師利菩薩祕密心真言</rdg></app></cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb n="0709a09" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0709a10" ed="T"/><byline cb:type="Translator"><note n="0709005" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（開府…寺）三十七字＝（唐北天竺）四字【明】，（大興善寺）四字【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><note n="0709005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（開府…寺）三十七字【大】，唐北天竺【明】，大興善寺【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app cb:word-count="37" n="0709005"><lem wit="【大】">開府儀同三司特進試鴻臚卿肅國
<lb n="0709a11" ed="T"/>公食邑三千戶賜紫贈司空諡大鑒
<lb n="0709a12" ed="T"/>正號大廣智大興善寺</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">唐北天竺</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】">大興善寺</rdg></app>三藏沙<note n="0709006" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">門＋（大廣智）【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><note n="0709006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">門【大】，門大廣智【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0709006"><lem wit="【大】">門</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】">門大廣智</rdg></app>
<lb n="0709a13" ed="T"/>不空奉　詔譯</byline>
<lb n="0709a14" ed="T"/><cb:div type="jing"><p xml:id="pT20p0709a1401">爾時金剛手菩薩摩訶薩等一切菩薩。皆於
<lb n="0709a15" ed="T"/>毘盧遮那佛前。各自說心真言印。於是曼殊
<lb n="0709a16" ed="T"/>室<note n="0709007" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">唎＝利【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><note n="0709007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">唎【大】，利【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0709007"><lem wit="【大】">唎</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】">利</rdg></app>菩薩摩訶薩。從座而起白佛言。世尊我
<lb n="0709a17" ed="T"/>今為欲利益未來一切諸有情故。速得成就
<lb n="0709a18" ed="T"/>摩訶般若波羅蜜多。若人纔誦一遍。如誦八
<lb n="0709a19" ed="T"/><note n="0709008" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">萬＝十【甲】</note><note n="0709008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">萬【大】，十【甲】</note><app n="0709008"><lem wit="【大】">萬</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">十</rdg></app>四千十二圍陀藏經。若誦兩遍。文殊師利
<lb n="0709a20" ed="T"/>普賢隨逐。四眾圍遶加<note n="0709009" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">被＝備【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><note n="0709009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">被【大】，備【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0709009"><lem wit="【大】">被</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】">備</rdg></app>。是慈無畏護法
<lb n="0709a21" ed="T"/>善神在其人前。阿難白文殊師利言。當說此
<lb n="0709a22" ed="T"/>真言。時<note n="0709010" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔有〕－【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><note n="0709010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">有【大】，〔－〕【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0709010"><lem wit="【大】">有</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>十萬億佛現。如是諸佛一一毛孔
<lb n="0709a23" ed="T"/>出十萬億菩薩。一一菩薩毛孔<note n="0709011" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔各〕－【乙】【丙】</note><note n="0709011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">各【大】，〔－〕【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0709011"><lem wit="【大】">各</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】【丙】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>出十萬億
<lb n="0709a24" ed="T"/>龍王。一一龍王毛孔各出十萬億龍女。一一
<lb n="0709a25" ed="T"/>龍女毛孔復出十萬億青象。一一青象毛孔
<lb n="0709a26" ed="T"/>各出十萬億白象。一一白象毛孔各出十萬
<lb n="0709a27" ed="T"/>億香象。一一香象毛孔<note n="0709012" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔復出…孔〕十三字－【甲】</note><note n="0709012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（復出…孔）十三字【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app cb:word-count="13" n="0709012"><lem wit="【大】">復出十萬億山象。一
<lb n="0709a28" ed="T"/>一山象毛孔</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>。復<note n="0709013" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">現＝出【甲】【乙】【丙】＊</note><note n="0709013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">現【大】＊，出【甲】【乙】【丙】＊</note><app n="0709013"><lem wit="【大】">現</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】">出</rdg></app>十萬億寶院。一一寶院
<lb n="0709a29" ed="T"/>復<app type="star" corresp="#0709013"><lem wit="【大】">現</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】">出</rdg></app>十萬億八功德水池。<note n="0709014" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔其〕－【甲】</note><note n="0709014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">其【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0709014"><lem wit="【大】">其</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>池四寶合成。
<pb n="0709b" xml:id="T20.1172.0709b" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0709b01" ed="T"/>一一寶池皆出十萬億閻浮檀金光。復於一
<lb n="0709b02" ed="T"/>一光中皆現十萬億圓光。<note n="0709015" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔一一〕－【甲】，〔一一圓光〕－【丙】</note><note n="0709015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">一一圓光【大】，〔－〕【丙】，圓光【甲】</note><app n="0709015"><lem wit="【大】">一一圓光</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">圓光</rdg></app>化出十
<lb n="0709b03" ed="T"/>萬<note n="0709016" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔億〕－【明】</note><note n="0709016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">億【大】，〔－〕【明】</note><app n="0709016"><lem wit="【大】">億</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>天女。嚴持種種供養。如是殑伽沙數四
<lb n="0709b04" ed="T"/>眾。一時共集大<note n="0709017" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">會＝集【丙】</note><note n="0709017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">會【大】，集【丙】</note><app n="0709017"><lem wit="【大】">會</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">集</rdg></app>。同音說此真言。<note n="0709018" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">現＝證【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><note n="0709018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">現【大】，證【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0709018"><lem wit="【大】">現</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】">證</rdg></app>三摩
<lb n="0709b05" ed="T"/>地三昧。我今略說少耳。知其功德無量。即說
<lb n="0709b06" ed="T"/>五字真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0709b07" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0709b0701" cb:type="dharani">阿<note n="0709019" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">囉＝羅【乙】【丙】＊</note><note n="0709019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">囉【大】＊，羅【乙】【丙】＊</note><app n="0709019"><lem wit="【大】">囉</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】【丙】">羅</rdg></app>跛左<note n="0709020" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">曩＝娜【甲】【乙】【丙】＊</note><note n="0709020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">曩【大】＊，娜【甲】【乙】【丙】＊</note><app n="0709020"><lem wit="【大】">曩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】">娜</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0709b08" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0709b0801">若善男子善女人。<note n="0709021" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">有＝若【乙】【丙】</note><note n="0709021" resp="CBETA" type="mod">有【大】，若【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0709021"><lem wit="【大】">有</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】【丙】">若</rdg></app>能持此真言。纔誦一遍
<lb n="0709b09" ed="T"/>即入如來一切法平等。一切文字亦皆平等。
<lb n="0709b10" ed="T"/>速得成就摩訶般若。為諸弟子<note n="0709022" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">受＝授【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><note n="0709022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">受【大】，授【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0709022"><lem wit="【大】">受</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】">授</rdg></app>此心真言
<lb n="0709b11" ed="T"/>時。令結密印。以二手金剛縛。並建忍願屈上
<lb n="0709b12" ed="T"/>節如劍形。印上<note n="0709023" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">承＝盛【明】</note><note n="0709023" resp="CBETA" type="mod">承【大】，盛【明】</note><app n="0709023"><lem wit="【大】">承</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">盛</rdg></app>華散壇供養。然應告<note n="0709024" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔言〕－【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><note n="0709024" resp="CBETA" type="mod">言【大】，〔－〕【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0709024"><lem wit="【大】">言</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>。
<lb n="0709b13" ed="T"/>此<note n="0709025" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔心〕－【明】</note><note n="0709025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">心【大】，〔－〕【明】</note><app n="0709025"><lem wit="【大】">心</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>法門一切如來祕密最勝。慎勿輕爾為
<lb n="0709b14" ed="T"/>愚人說。破汝三昧戒。善諦思惟。</p>
<lb n="0709b15" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0709b1501">阿者是無生義。</p>
<lb n="0709b16" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0709b1601"><app type="star" corresp="#0709019"><lem wit="【大】">囉</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】【丙】">羅</rdg></app><note n="0709026" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔者〕－【甲】＊</note><note n="0709026" resp="CBETA" type="mod">者【大】＊，〔－〕【甲】＊</note><app n="0709026"><lem wit="【大】">者</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>清淨無染離塵垢義。</p>
<lb n="0709b17" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0709b1701">跛<app type="star" corresp="#0709026"><lem wit="【大】">者</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>亦無第一義諦諸法平等義。</p>
<lb n="0709b18" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0709b1801">左者諸法無有諸行義。</p>
<lb n="0709b19" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0709b1901"><app type="star" corresp="#0709020"><lem wit="【大】">曩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】">娜</rdg></app>者諸法無有性相。<note n="0709027" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">說言＝言說【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><note n="0709027" resp="CBETA" type="mod">說言【大】，言說【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0709027"><lem wit="【大】">說言</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】">言說</rdg></app>文字皆不可得
<lb n="0709b20" ed="T"/>義。</p>
<lb n="0709b21" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0709b2101">以<app type="star" corresp="#0709020"><lem wit="【大】">曩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】">娜</rdg></app>字無有性相故。左字無有諸行。以左
<lb n="0709b22" ed="T"/>字<note n="0709028" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">無＋（有）【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><note n="0709028" resp="CBETA" type="mod">無【大】，無有【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0709028"><lem wit="【大】">無</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】">無有</rdg></app>諸行故。跛字無第一義諦。以跛字無
<lb n="0709b23" ed="T"/><note n="0709029" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔第一義〕－【甲】</note><note n="0709029" resp="CBETA" type="mod">第一義【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0709029"><lem wit="【大】">第一義</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>諦故。<app type="star" corresp="#0709019"><lem wit="【大】">囉</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】【丙】">羅</rdg></app>字無有塵垢。以<app type="star" corresp="#0709019"><lem wit="【大】">囉</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】【丙】">羅</rdg></app>字無有
<lb n="0709b24" ed="T"/>塵垢故。阿字法本不生義。善男子當觀是心
<lb n="0709b25" ed="T"/>本來清淨無所染著。離我我所分別之相。入
<lb n="0709b26" ed="T"/>此門者名三摩地。是真修習。當<note n="0709030" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔知〕－【甲】</note><note n="0709030" resp="CBETA" type="mod">知【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0709030"><lem wit="【大】">知</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>是人如
<lb n="0709b27" ed="T"/>來印可。殊勝功德不可思議。若誦一遍能<note n="0709031" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">除＝徐【明】</note><note n="0709031" resp="CBETA" type="mod">除【大】，徐【明】</note><app n="0709031"><lem wit="【大】">除</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">徐</rdg></app>
<lb n="0709b28" ed="T"/>行<note n="0709032" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">人＝者【明】</note><note n="0709032" resp="CBETA" type="mod">人【大】，者【明】</note><app n="0709032"><lem wit="【大】">人</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">者</rdg></app>一切苦難。若誦<note n="0709033" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">兩＝二【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><note n="0709033" resp="CBETA" type="mod">兩【大】，二【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0709033"><lem wit="【大】">兩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】">二</rdg></app>遍除滅億劫生死
<lb n="0709b29" ed="T"/>重罪。若誦三遍三昧現前。若誦四遍總持不
<pb n="0709c" xml:id="T20.1172.0709c" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0709c01" ed="T"/>忘。若誦五遍速成無上菩提。若能一心獨處
<lb n="0709c02" ed="T"/>閑靜。梵書五字輪壇。依法念誦滿一月已。曼
<lb n="0709c03" ed="T"/>殊菩薩即現其身。或於空中演說法要。是時
<lb n="0709c04" ed="T"/>行者得宿命智。辯才無礙神足自在。勝願成
<lb n="0709c05" ed="T"/>就福智具足。速能<note n="0709034" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">階＝諧【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><note n="0709034" resp="CBETA" type="mod">階【大】，諧【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0709034"><lem wit="【大】">階</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】">諧</rdg></app>證如來法身。但心信
<lb n="0709c06" ed="T"/>受。經十六生決成正覺。若<note n="0709035" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔力〕－【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><note n="0709035" resp="CBETA" type="mod">力【大】，〔－〕【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0709035"><lem wit="【大】">力</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>不辦建<note n="0709036" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔立〕－【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><note n="0709036" resp="CBETA" type="mod">立【大】，〔－〕【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0709036"><lem wit="【大】">立</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>壇
<lb n="0709c07" ed="T"/>場。香花供養及<note n="0709037" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">畫＝書【甲】</note><note n="0709037" resp="CBETA" type="mod">畫【大】，書【甲】</note><app n="0709037"><lem wit="【大】">畫</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">書</rdg></app>本尊。以用香泥塗舍利
<lb n="0709c08" ed="T"/>塔。梵寫五字真言。旋遶念誦五十萬遍。文殊
<lb n="0709c09" ed="T"/>菩薩現其<note n="0709038" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔人〕－【甲】【丙】</note><note n="0709038" resp="CBETA" type="mod">人【大】，〔－〕【甲】【丙】</note><app n="0709038"><lem wit="【大】">人</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【丙】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>前而為說法。當得宿命辯才。一
<lb n="0709c10" ed="T"/>切如來諸菩薩等。及執金剛恒沙聖眾。常加
<lb n="0709c11" ed="T"/>護念速滿諸願。疾證菩<note n="0709039" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">提＋（修習儀軌頂經廣說）八字【乙】</note><note n="0709039" resp="CBETA" type="mod">提【大】，提修習儀軌頂經廣說【乙】</note><app n="0709039"><lem wit="【大】">提</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">提修習儀軌頂經廣說</rdg></app>。<note n="0709040" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔廣如…說〕七字－【甲】</note><note n="0709040" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（廣如…說）七字【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app cb:word-count="7" n="0709040"><lem wit="【大】">廣如金剛頂經
<lb n="0709c12" ed="T"/>說</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>。</p>
<lb n="0709c13" ed="T"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="close"><cb:jhead><note n="0709041" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">金剛乃至卷十九字甲本無之而有次文，經云文殊師利常住東北清涼山一萬菩薩以為眷族又云一切諸佛之母於三世中能現三世中能現三寶又云過去已成佛道號龍種上智尊王如來又云現在北方今成佛道號歡喜藏摩尼寶積如來又云未來當成佛道號普見如來又云一切如來般若藏又云供養文殊所得福報尚勝供養一切諸佛又云若有眾生聞文殊名除却十二億生死之罪若禮拜供養者生生之處但生諸佛家為文殊師利威神所護云云，長治二年九月日辰時書之百七十五字，（錄云）＋金【乙】</note><note n="0709041" resp="CBETA" type="mod">金剛頂超勝三界經說文殊五字真言勝相一卷【大】，（經云文殊師利常住東北清涼山一萬菩薩以為眷族又云一切諸佛之母於三世中能現三世中能現三寶又云過去已成佛道號龍種上智尊王如來又云現在北方今成佛道號歡喜藏摩尼寶積如來又云未來當成佛道號普見如來又云一切如來般若藏又云供養文殊所得福報尚勝供養一切諸佛又云若有眾生聞文殊名除却十二億生死之罪若禮拜供養者生生之處但生諸佛家為文殊師利威神所護云云，長治二年九月日辰時書之）百七十五字【甲】，錄云金剛頂超勝三界經說文殊五字真言勝相一卷【乙】</note><app n="0709041"><lem wit="【大】">金剛頂超勝三界經說文殊五字真<note n="0709042" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔言〕－【明】</note><note n="0709042" resp="CBETA" type="mod">言【大】，〔－〕【明】</note><app n="0709042"><lem wit="【大】">言</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app><note n="0709043" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔勝相一卷〕－【丙】，丙本奧書曰久安二年卯月十九日酉時於高野往生院別所書了，成蓮房阿闍梨御房奉受了</note><note n="0709043" resp="CBETA" type="mod">勝相一卷【大】，〔－〕【丙】，丙本奧書曰久安二年卯月十九日酉時於高野往生院別所書了，成蓮房阿闍梨御房奉受了</note><app n="0709043"><lem wit="【大】">勝
